---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import { CONTACT_EMAIL, SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title={`${SITE_TITLE} | About`}
      description="About Michael Janan and how to get in touch."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Michael. This is version about 12 of my website but I have a
        good feeling about this one. You haven't heard of me in 2026 but I'm
        hoping you might start seeing my work.
      </p>
      <p>
        I write here about the things I keep coming back to — science fiction,
        economics, politics, and the places where they overlap. This is where I
        think out loud and, hopefully, start a few conversations. You can expect
        to see a mix of ideas I'd like to share and discuss, more detailed
        analyses using data, updates on creative endeavours and some
        reflections.
      </p>
      <p>
        <!-- Replace this with a short professional bio: what you do, your
             background, and what readers can expect from your writing. -->
        I'm currently working on a handful of projects you can read about on the
        <a href="/projects">projects</a> page.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        The best way to reach me is by email. I read everything and try to
        reply.
      </p>
      <p class="contact">
        <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
        <br />
        <span
          >Technically Janan is only my middle name but its a bit less common to
          write under</span
        >
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  h2 {
    margin-top: 2em;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }
  .contact a {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
